12:29.840 --> 12:33.840
It's absolute. It's all inclusive.

12:33.840 --> 12:39.840
It's unanswerable and oddly for a religion that makes such large claims.

12:39.840 --> 12:41.840
Notice another thing about Islam.

12:41.840 --> 12:47.840
