12:57.840 --> 13:01.840
With Islam, a younger religion and perhaps therefore more on its first flush,

13:01.840 --> 13:08.840
there's an extraordinarily strong willingness to say that any challenge to its absolutist claims

13:08.840 --> 13:10.840
is by definition profane.

13:11.840 --> 13:15.840
